<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.9.11">
<l>ucci yuḷḷē niṟkun tēva tēvaṟkuk kaṇṇa pirāṟ</l>
<l>kiccai yuḷcel lavuṇartti vaṇkuru kūrccaṭa kōpa</l>
<l>ṉiccoṉṉa vāyirat tuḷivai yummōr pattem pirāṟku</l>
<l>niccalum viṇṇap pamceyya nīḷkaḻal ceṉṉi porumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When announcing [you] go into service to lord Kaṇṇaṉ,</l>
<l>the god of gods who stands on top, [and] making a petition perpetually</l>
<l>to our lord by this one decade in these thousand spoken by Caṭakōpaṉ</l>
<l>from liberal Kurukūr, the head will beat against [his feet with] long anklets.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
